            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E5%8A%BF%E5%A4%B4%E5%87%8F%E7%BC%93%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E5%8A%BF%E5%A4%B4%E5%87%8F%E7%BC%93%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#近期新冠报告病例上升势头减缓#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%A7%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E8%BF%98%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%A7%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#国内还会出现规模性疫情吗#</span></a> 中国疾控中心监测数据显示，4月中下旬以来，全国报告的新冠病毒感染确诊病例呈现上升趋势，但最近一周上升势头有所减缓。北京、上海等地有关专家注意到，本轮新冠病毒感染患者主要表现仍为发热、咳嗽，症状普遍较轻、病程较短。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫疫点通#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4902679185653827" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly8he2a1f5iu5j60zk0k0wjd02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/vdvhQFmelx085wPcuyvK01041200uQ2g0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0